Cuando las preocupaciones son persistentes y repetitivos pueden llegar a convertirse en una forma habitual de enfrentarse a las situaciones, el sujeto puede estar sufriendo de Trastorno de ansiedad generalizada (tag). Los expertos consideran que el TAG probablemente causado por una combinación de factores: biológicos, psicológicos y el resultado de eventos azarosos de la vida. Los que sufren de TAG frecuentemente también sufren a menudo de algún otro trastorno por ejemplo, la Depresión o Trastorno de Pánico debido a la vulnerabilidad de preocuparse. Parecería ser que la influencia genética es un componente indispensable al desarrollo de  Trastornos de ansiedad. Robert Ronning founded PayVida after seeing firsthand the need for a simpler means of getting paid. As an experienced businessperson and PayVida’s Director of Strategic Development, he’s witnessed the challenges that businesses face with getting paid. Oftentimes, it can seem like simply getting paid on time and in full can take nothing short of a miracle. Clients forget, primary account contacts go on leave, errors happen. And while it’s tempting to want to give your clients and customers as many means of payment as possible, having five different payment methods makes accounting much more difficult than it has to be.

That’s why Ronning created PayVida. PayVida is an all-in-one payment solution that makes it easy to track and organize all of your non-cash payments. With PayVida, you can easily process credit cards, debit cards, PayPal, Apple Pay, E-transfers, and even gift cards. Best yet, all of your transactions show up in one place.

Running an online business? PayVida’s e-commerce portal offers hosted payment pages that allow you to easily collect payments from customers. You can integrate these pages with your existing e-commerce solution to give them a better user experience, or simply use PayVida’s payment collection service to receive payment.

Business isn’t simple anymore – but your payment solution can be. With PayVida, you get a powerful solution that’s easy to use.
